    Title: Bhagavad-Gitâ
    Locus: III 27
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
---
All actions are performed by the Gunas, born of Prakriti. One whose
understanding is deluded by egoism alone thinks： ‘I am the doer.’
